1. `global/config/musicbrainz/MusicBrainzHttpClientConfig.kt` 생성:
```kotlin
@Configuration
@EnableConfigurationProperties(MusicBrainzApiProperties::class)
class MusicBrainzHttpClientConfig(
    private val properties: MusicBrainzApiProperties,
) {
    @Bean
    fun musicBrainzHttpClient(): HttpClient =
        HttpClient(CIO) {
            expectSuccess = false
            install(ContentNegotiation) {
                jackson {
                    registerModule(KotlinModule.Builder().build())
                    configure(DeserializationFeature.FAIL_ON_UNKNOWN_PROPERTIES, false)
                }
            }
            install(DefaultRequest) {
                header(HttpHeaders.UserAgent, "${properties.userAgent} ( ${properties.contact} )")
                header(HttpHeaders.Accept, "application/json")
            }
        }
}
```

2. User-Agent 형식: `AppName/Version ( contact-email )` — MusicBrainz 정책 준수
3. Jackson 설정: unknown properties 무시, Kotlin 모듈 등록
4. expectSuccess=false: 4xx/5xx도 예외 없이 받아서 호출부에서 처리

